## üé® **9 - Mudar Cor de Fundo com Bot√£o**
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Mudar Cor de Fundo</title>
</head>
<body>
    <button onclick="mudarCor()">Mudar Cor</button>

    <script>
        function mudarCor() {
            document.body.style.backgroundColor = 'lightblue';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
